 education 


ph.d.  computer science, university of washington         1991 
m.s.   computer science, university of washinton          1988 
b.s.   electrical and electronic engineering,             1984
       national technical university of athens, greece              

 research interests 

scalable parallel architectures, interconnection networks, 
routing algorithms, communication protocols and 
parallel computer interfaces.



